metadata.name: THE JOURNEY OF THE ITINERANT
metadata.description:
THE JOURNEY OF THE ITINERANT.

A long journey ahead.  
The red sun.  
The gigantic mountains. 
A peaceful mind.

I like travelling alone. It gives me the joy of understanding myself and realising the fact that i am just a mere human being in this earth with endless possibilities and there is nothing in my life to be arrogant of.

The beauty of earth never ceases to amaze me.

I wish I could see atleast 0.5% of this beautiful creation before i die.



1/1 By Mr.Minimalo
